title: Noventa Stratocaster
description: Combining classic Fender style and dynamic single-coil pickups, the Noventa series delivers powerful tones, modern playability and dashing good looks.

title: Tom Morello Stratocaster
description: Tom Morello's unique, powerful sounds - from gentle rhythms to screaming feedback, chaotic stutters, and more.

title: Vintera Road Worn 50's Stratocaster
description: Finished in nitrocellulose lacquer – prized for its natural tonal qualities and distinct aging patterns, then hand-distressed for an authentically broken-in look, this Strat® delivers the bell-like tone and playing comfort you’d expect from a great vintage guitar.
